&lt;p&gt;Weedmaps is seeking an Associate Creative Director, Design to help define and evolve the visual future of the Weedmaps brand across campaigns, social media, editorial content, lifecycle marketing, product storytelling, and emerging AI-enabled creative systems. This role combines creative leadership, visual storytelling, and systems thinking. The Associate Creative Director, Design will lead concept development, establish scalable design frameworks, mentor creative talent, and partner cross-functionally to ensure Weedmaps delivers visually distinctive, culturally relevant, and high-performing creative work across every consumer touchpoint.&lt;/p&gt;
