&lt;li&gt;Build scalable design systems and modular creative frameworks that support rapid iteration and cross-channel deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide social-first creative optimized for Instagram, TikTok, short-form video, and emerging platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Production teams to improve creative workflows and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explore and implement AI-assisted design workflows that improve speed, scalability, and creative effectiveness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain awareness of design trends, internet culture, platform behaviors, and emerging technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide creative leadership and direction to designers, freelancers, contractors, and production partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and develop creative talent through coaching, feedback, and professional development.&lt;/li&gt;
