&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Creative Leadership on resource planning, staffing needs, and workflow prioritization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of creative excellence, innovation, collaboration, and accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to long-term creative vision and organizational development initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
