&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in design, art direction, or creative leadership roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong portfolio demonstrating excellence across campaigns, social content, digital storytelling, and brand systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading multidisciplinary creative projects across multiple channels and platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of typography, layout, motion, visual storytelling, and modern design systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience collaborating with cross-functional stakeholders in fast-paced creative environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of social-first creative development and platform-native content creation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
