&lt;p&gt;See how we’ve grown—our journey, leadership team, and what’s next at&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://weedmaps.com/corporate&quot;&gt;Weedmaps.com/corporate&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Weedmaps:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2008, we’ve grown from a small startup to a global leader in the cannabis industry.&amp;nbsp; Our dedication to transparency, education, and community has set us apart, and today, we proudly serve cannabis to consumers and businesses in the U.S. and worldwide.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
